1. *Leti* ptičica visoko u nebo. (The little bird *flies* high into the sky.)
2. Vreme *leti* kada se dobro zabavljamo. (Time *flies* when we're having fun.)
3. Čuo sam da će avion *leteti* u 8 ujutru. (I heard that the airplane will *fly* at 8 in the morning.)
4. Na ulici *lete* novine i smeće. (On the street, *papers* and garbage *are flying*.)
5. Deca *lete* zmajeve na livadi. (Children *fly* kites in the meadow.)
6. *Letimo* avionom preko planina. (We are *flying* over the mountains in the airplane.)
7. *Letela* je lopta preko ograde. (The ball *flew* over the fence.)
8. Želim da *letim* kao ptica. (I wish to *fly* like a bird.)
9. Vetar *leti* kroz prozor. (The wind *blows* through the window.)
10. *Leteli* su golubovi oko krova. (The pigeons *flew* around the roof.)